#: product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce.php
msgid "https://revenuehunt.com/"
msgstr "https://revenuehunt.com/"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:67
msgid "WooCommerce"
msgstr "WooCommerce"

#. translators: %s: link to the WooCommerce plugin on wordpress.org (anchor text "WooCommerce").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:75
#, php-format
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires the WooCommerce plugin to be installed and active. You can download %s here. If you want this plugin developed for your eCommerce platform, please send us a message."
msgstr "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce vereist dat de WooCommerce plugin is geïnstalleerd en actief is. Je kan deze downloaden %s hier. Als je wil dat deze plugin ontwikkeld voor je e-commerce platform, stuur ons dan een bericht."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:95
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires your website to have a valid HTTPS/SSL certificate."
msgstr "Product Recommendation Quiz voor eCommerce vereist dat je website een geldig HTTPS/SSL-certificaat heeft."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:109
msgid "This plugin does not work on local environments. It needs to be installed on a live website. Your website needs to be public and not hidden by a site under construction plugin because it needs connection to our server in order to work."
msgstr "Deze plugin werkt niet op lokale omgevingen. Het moet worden geïnstalleerd op een live website. Je website moet openbaar zijn en niet verborgen door een website in aanbouw plugin omdat het verbinding met onze server nodig heeft om te werken."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:124
msgid "Settings > Permalinks"
msgstr "Instellingen > Permalinks"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:127
msgid "Your current permalink structure is set to \"Plain\". For this plugin to authenticate correctly, a different permalink structure (such as \"Post name\") is required."
msgstr "Je huidige permalink structuur staat ingesteld op \"Eenvoudig\". Voor deze plugin is een andere permalink structuur (zoals \"Berichtnaam\") vereist om correct te kunnen authenticeren."

#. translators: %s: link to the WordPress "Settings > Permalinks" screen.
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:133
#, php-format
msgid "Please update your permalink settings under %s to ensure seamless authentication."
msgstr "Werk je permalink instellingen bij onder %s om naadloze authenticatie te garanderen."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:154
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:185
msgid "here"
msgstr "hier"

#. translators: %s: link to the troubleshooting FAQ (anchor text "here").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:162
#, php-format
msgid "There's an issue with the WPML Multilingual CMS plugin which interferes with the authentication process of other plugins. Please deactivate the WPML Multilingual CMS plugin temporarily, you can reactivate it later. More info %s."
msgstr "Er is een probleem met de WPML Multilingual CMS plugin die het authenticatieproces van andere plugins verstoort. Gelieve de WPML Multilingual CMS plugin tijdelijk te deactiveren, je kan deze later opnieuw activeren. Meer informatie %s."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:183
msgid "WordPress REST API"
msgstr "WordPress REST-API"

#. translators: 1: link to the WordPress REST API docs (anchor "WordPress REST API"); 2: link to the troubleshooting FAQ (anchor "here").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:193
#, php-format
msgid "It seems like there's something interfering with your %1$s. This needs to be fixed in order to grant access to this plugin. More info %2$s. We're getting the following error accessing your WooCommerce API from our server:"
msgstr "Het lijkt erop dat er iets tussenkomt in je %1$s. Dit moet hersteld worden om toegang tot deze plugin te krijgen. Meer informatie %2$s. We krijgen de volgende foutmelding bij het benaderen van je WooCommerce API vanaf onze server:"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:216
msgid "The following REST API endpoint is returning a valid JSON but the returned content-type is text/html instead of the expected application/json:"
msgstr "Het volgende REST API eindpunt retourneert een geldige JSON maar het geretourneerde inhoudstype is teskt/html in plaats van het verwachte application/json:"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:248
msgid "contact us"
msgstr "contacteer ons"

#. translators: 1: previous store domain; 2: new store domain.
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:255
#, php-format
msgid "We've detected that you've changed the domain name. We're migrating your Product Recommendation Quiz account from %1$s to %2$s"
msgstr "We hebben gedetecteerd dat je de domeinnaam heeft veranderd. We migreren je Product Recommendation Quiz account van %1$s tot %2$s"

#. translators: %s: link to the RevenueHunt contact page (anchor "contact us").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:266
#, php-format
msgid "Please %s if you encounter any issues."
msgstr "Gelieve %s als je problemen ondervindt."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-menu.php:106
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz"
msgstr "Productaanbevelingsquiz"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-menu.php:107
msgid "Product Quiz"
msgstr "Productquiz"

#. translators: %s: link to the RevenueHunt website (anchor "RevenueHunt").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:92
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:122
#, php-format
msgid "by %s"
msgstr "door %s"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:131
msgid "Congratulations!"
msgstr "Gefeliciteerd!"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:132
msgid "You're one step away from getting more conversions and sales in your store."
msgstr "Je bent één stap verwijderd van meer conversies en verkoop in je winkel."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:133
msgid "We just need you to grant this plugin permission to access your WooCommerce store:"
msgstr "We hoeven alleen maar je deze plugin toestemming te geven voor toegang tot je WooCommerce winkel:"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:135
msgid "grant permission now"
msgstr "rechten nu toekennen"

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-page.php:140
msgid "this article"
msgstr "dit artikel"

#. translators: %s: link to the troubleshooting article (anchor "this article").
